name: Hickory Dickory Dock & Baa Baa Black Sheep
overview: Hickory Dickory Dock / Baa, Baa, Black Sheep is a 1-player sliding block puzzle. Players can chose a picture based upon either nursery rhyme. The sliding block puzzle can be 3 x 3, 4 x 4, 5 x 5, or 6 x 6. The player can choose from 6 levels of difficulty, which determines the level of mixing prior to starting a game.
